# NEVPNConnectionError.pluginDisabled

**Case**

An error code that indicates the VPN plugin isn’t available or needs an update.

## Declaration

```swift
case pluginDisabled
```

## Plugin error codes

- **NEVPNConnectionError.pluginFailed**: An error code that indicates the VPN plugin failed unexpectedly.
